Class CafeteriaController

java.lang.Object
controller.CafeteriaController
public class CafeteriaController extends Object
The CafeteriaController class is responsible for controlling the simulation of the cafeteria. It interacts with the GUI and the simulation engine to manage the simulation flow and update the GUI.
